SECRET_KEY=your_super_secret_key_here
ALGORITHM=HS256
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=60

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:nizom123@localhost/tibbiyot
```

> Generate a strong secret key with: `openssl rand -hex 32`

